    source_url: "https://www.paragraf.rs/propisi/zakon_o_nasledjivanju.html",
    text_local: "Nasleđuje se zaostavština.\n\nZaostavštinu čine sva nasleđivanju podobna prava koja su ostaviocu pripadala u trenutku smrti.\n\nZaostavštinu ne čine predmeti domaćinstva manje vrednosti (pokućstvo, nameštaj, posteljina i slično) koji služe svakodnevnim potrebama ostaviočevih potomaka, njegovog bračnog druga i roditelja, ako su sa ostaviocem živeli u istom domaćinstvu, već oni postaju zajednička svojina ovih lica.\n\nZaostavštinu ne čine dobra za koja su ostaviočevu imovinu uvećali njegovi potomci koji su s njime živeli u zajednici i svojim trudom, zaradom ili inače mu pomagali u privređivanju, već ta dobra pripadaju potomku, srazmerno delu za koji je uvećao ostaviočevu imovinu.",
    text: "The estate is inherited.\n\nThe estate consists of all inheritable rights that belonged to the decedent at the time of death.\n\nThe estate does not include household items of lesser value (furniture, furnishings, bedding, etc.) that serve the daily needs of the decedent's descendants, spouse, and parents, if they lived in the same household with the decedent; these items become the joint property of these individuals.\n\nThe estate does not include assets that were increased by the decedent's descendants who lived in the community with him and assisted him in earning a living through their efforts, earnings, or otherwise; rather, these assets belong to the descendant in proportion to the part by which they increased the decedent's estate.",
