    text: "The second order of inheritance consists of the decedent's spouse and the decedent's parents and their descendants.\n\nThe decedent's spouse inherits half of the estate, while the other half is inherited in equal parts by the decedent's parents.\n\nIf the decedent's spouse cannot or will not inherit, the estate is inherited in equal parts by the decedent's parents.",
