    source_url: "https://www.zakon.hr/z/87/Zakon-o-naslje%C4%91ivanju",
    text_local: "Raspolaganje namijenjenom stvari\n\nSvako kasnije oporučiteljevo voljno raspolaganje stvarju ili pravom koje je bio nekome oporukom namijenio smatra se opozivom namjene te stvari, odnosno prava.",
    text: "Disposition of intended property\n\nAny later voluntary disposition by the testator of property or rights that were intended for someone by will is considered a revocation of the designation of that property or right.",
